  "label": "The Saltflux Instrument Shop",
  "description": "The Saltflux Instrument Shop serves as a precision workshop set into Brineshade Terminator City’s fused basalt platform, its walls lined with salt-cemented shelving and sealed tool lockers. Long, matte-black benches sit beneath louvered light baffles that admit controlled bands of Saltharrow’s hard white radiance without glare. A recessed calibration bay anchors the rear of the room, built on vibration-damped footings engineered against the city’s measurable tidal stresses. Mineral haze filters and airtight shutters maintain optical clarity and corrosion resistance in the thin, brine-laden air.",
